description.text: One person killed and another died from a heart attack, 37 people injured, 369 buildings destroyed and 2,548 damaged and power outages occurred in Duzce. Twenty-six people injured in Sakarya, 14 in Bolu, 10 in Zonguldak, 4 in Bursa and 2 in Istanbul.
